description:
Who was the first prophet mentioned in the Bible, and what makes Moses stand out among the prophets of Israel? Uncover the foundational role of Abraham as the Bible's first prophet and delve into the unparalleled leadership of Moses, who communicated with God face to face. Join us as we trace the lineage of prophecy in Israel's history, highlighting the enduring impact of these prophetic leaders on the faith journey of God's people.

To watch the full video from Elder Ted Wilson, president of the General Conference of Seventh-day Adventists, paste this link into your browser:
https://youtu.be/xdPLmZ7K4sQ
